# Codebase reference (supplement)

## Important paths

| Area | Location |
|------|----------|
| Root layout / auth routing | `app/_layout.tsx` |
| Trial/subscription store | `store/subscriptionStore.ts` |
| Trial service | `lib/trial.ts` |
| Subscribe / expired trial UI | `app/subscribe.tsx` |
| Trial banner | `components/TrialBanner.tsx` |
| DB migration (trials) | `scripts/apply-user-trials-migration.sql` |
| App config / build numbers | `app.json` |
| Supabase client | `lib/supabase/` |
| Migrations | `supabase/migrations/` |

## Trial / subscription flow

- `useSubscriptionStore.checkSubscription()` — Supabase for trial dates, RevenueCat for paid entitlements (`The Homeschool Hub Pro`)
- Apply trial migration via SQL Editor or `supabase db push` (`ensure_user_trial`, `convert_user_trial` RPCs)

## Builds

- Version/build in `app.json` (`version`, `ios.buildNumber`, `android.versionCode`)
- EAS: `eas.json` — `appVersionSource: local`, no auto-increment
- RevenueCat skipped in Expo Go; use production/TestFlight builds to test IAP
